	(4555,817,'_cover_image','field_594147ada3a9f'),
	(4556,817,'introduction','Get Up Speak Out is a 5 year (2016-2020) strategic partnership between the Netherlands MoFA and the GUSO consortium (dance4life, Rutgers, Simavi, Stop Aid Now, Choice and IPPF). GUSO is building on Access Skills and Knowledge (ASK) achievements and lessons learned implemented by the SRHR alliance. The GUSO project is implemented in Jinja and Mayuge districts.'),
